//! clap-noun-verb routes — GENERATED by `ggen sync` from the
//! `clap-noun-verb-pack` ontology (`cnv:Command` individuals). Do not edit
//! by hand: routes are a pure projection of the ontology; there is NO logic
//! slot here — business logic lives behind the stable seam in
//! `crate::verbs::handlers::*` (hand-written; a missing impl is a compile
//! error). To freeze this file against regeneration, add a comment
//! containing the literal marker "ggen" + ":" + "local-override" (written
//! apart here so this instructional comment doesn't itself trigger the
//! freeze).
//!
//! Pattern aligned with ~/clap-noun-verb's own authoritative pack
//! conventions (templates/verb.rs.tera): thin wrapper, typed args,
//! Rust-reserved-word raw-identifier escaping.

